data.description: Assumable VA 6.2% interest rate available. This exquisite two-story home is nestled in the exclusive gated community of Tuscany Heights, offering a sense of security and tranquility. The tasteful landscaping and charming stone and brick exterior create an inviting curb appeal that will impress anyone who visits. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a generously sized office, providing the perfect space for privacy and productivity. The open floor plan throughout the common areas features beautiful wood flooring and high ceilings, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere that is perfect for entertaining guests. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting stunning granite countertops, rich espresso-colored cabinetry, and modern stainless steel appliances. With a convenient walk-in pantry and gas cooking, this kitchen has everything you need for culinary adventures. Escape to the downstairs primary suite, where you'll find a luxurious en-suite that is sure to impress. Dual vanity sinks, a relaxing garden tub, a spacious walk-in shower, and a roomy walk-in closet provide ultimate comfort and convenience. Upstairs, you'll discover a huge game room/loft area that can be used for various purposes, whether it's a playroom for the kids or a space for entertaining friends. Additionally, there are three additional bedrooms, including two that are connected by a convenient jack-and-jill bathroom. Step outside and experience the beauty of the backyard in all weather conditions with the addition of a lovely sunroom equipped with a mini-split. You can relax and enjoy the outdoor space whether it's rain or shine. The property also offers a new roof and the solar panel system is paid off.
